{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/people/olivia-bailey","content_id":"d6a17b3c-e267-4014-b95b-e4881d814a20","description":"Olivia Bailey was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State (Minister for Early Education) and Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State (Minister for Equalities) at the Department for Education on 7 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Reading West and Mid Berkshire in July 2024.","details":{"body":"<p>Olivia Bailey was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State (Minister for Early Education) and Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State (Minister for Equalities) at the Department for Education on 7 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She was elected as the MP for Reading West and Mid Berkshire in July 2024.</p>\n","full_name":"Olivia Bailey MP","image":{"alt_text":"Olivia Bailey MP","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/68bd9abfcc8356c3c882ab9b/s465_olivia_bailey_portrait_960.jpeg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","first_published_at":"2025-09-07T15:46:23+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/olivia-bailey","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/olivia-bailey","base_path":"/government/people/olivia-bailey","content_id":"d6a17b3c-e267-4014-b95b-e4881d814a20","document_type":"person","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-09-22T12:19:53Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Olivia Bailey MP","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/olivia-bailey","withdrawn":false}],"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"7c16bd0f-9ace-423a-98e8-5ea2230a78b7","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":2,"started_on":"2025-09-07T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"person":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/olivia-bailey","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/olivia-bailey","base_path":"/government/people/olivia-bailey","content_id":"d6a17b3c-e267-4014-b95b-e4881d814a20","details":{"body":"<p>Olivia Bailey was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State (Minister for Early Education) and Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State (Minister for Equalities) at the Department for Education on 7 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She was elected as the MP for Reading West and Mid Berkshire in July 2024.</p>\n","image":{"alt_text":"Olivia Bailey MP","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/68bd9abfcc8356c3c882ab9b/s465_olivia_bailey_portrait_960.jpeg"}},"document_type":"person","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-09-22T12:19:53Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Olivia Bailey MP","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/olivia-bailey","withdrawn":false}],"role":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state--256","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state--256","base_path":"/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state--256","content_id":"d9972b0f-b836-4161-825e-004db0281512","details":{"body":"<p>The minister’s responsibilities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>early years education including for children with special educational needs and disabilities (SEND)</li>\n  <li>childcare and the home learning environment</li>\n  <li>early years workforce</li>\n  <li>early communication skills and early intervention</li>\n  <li>Best Start Family Hubs and parenting</li>\n  <li>breakfast clubs</li>\n  <li>school food, including free school meals</li>\n  <li>holiday activities and food (HAF) programme</li>\n  <li>school attendance, including register of children who are not in school</li>\n  <li>reception admissions</li>\n  <li>changes to existing schools</li>\n  <li>home-to-school transport</li>\n  <li>mental health support in schools</li>\n  <li>behaviour, preventing bullying and exclusions in schools</li>\n  <li>school uniform</li>\n  <li>young carers</li>\n  <li>independent schools</